              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10413488935910196319">Alistair Macleod was a complete and undeniable genius. His two books of short stories are among the best things I have ever read. I cannot single out any one story because they are all masterpieces in miniature. I highly recommend this collection. </span>

          </span>
