      <span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_review_2748099417'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it gr-button gr-button--small" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F116490.As_Birds_Bring_Forth_the_Sun_and_Other_Stories">Like</a></span>
