<span id="freeTextContainer1786996734585858391">Great short stories about life and lives, about human beings&apos;, animals&apos;, and human beings and animals&apos;. <br/><br/>These stories might not be so happy and the author does give any judgments of what has happened. But the truth of life, the surprise, the joy, the tragics, gaining and blessings, misfortune and losses are all revealed in front of you. <br/><br/>There is no formula for what kind of life we should live. Just live it and expect the least. </span>
