<span id="freeTextContainer18145855754755960654">It&apos;s a gentle (dare I say typically cliched Canadian) short story collection, that builds to its peak with the fabulous story &quot;The Tuning of Perfection&quot;. But then it&apos;s followed by two stories that did absolutely nothing for me, and didn&apos;t touch me in any way. The end result is your typical mixed back of a collection, but it&apos;s at least tied together by a beautiful &amp; delicate writing style.</span>
  <span id="freeText18145855754755960654" style="display:none">It's a gentle (dare I say typically cliched Canadian) short story collection, that builds to its peak with the fabulous story "The Tuning of Perfection". But then it's followed by two stories that did absolutely nothing for me, and didn't touch me in any way. The end result is your typical mixed back of a collection, but it's at least tied together by a beautiful &amp; delicate writing style.</span>
